<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's left her fans and admirers guessing as to whether she is indeed expecting her third child.</p>

<p>And model April Love Geary was again seen in a lovely pink ensemble in Malibu, California on Saturday morning, making an early grocery run so as to avoid the large weekend crowds.</p>

<p>The 25-year-old wife of Robin Thicke wore an empire waist dress in a soft-looking material that only amplified rumors that she looks pregnant.  </p>

<p>Errands: Model April Love Geary was again seen in a lovely pink ensemble in Malibu on Saturday morning, making an early grocery run so as to avoid the large weekend crowds</p>

<p>The 5ft11in beauty strode along behind her shopping cart with her blondish hair down, covering up with a pink floral face mask and thick sunglasses. </p>

<p>Geary's dress featured a wrapped bust and short sleeves, and the billowing skirt ended just below her knees. </p>

<p>The garment definitely fanned out, giving the impression of a growing baby bump underneath. </p>

