<p>To complete the look, April wore tan sandal flats.</p>

<p>Robin and April, who have been wed since 2014, already share two young children – daughters Mia Love, two, and Lola Alain, one. </p>

<p>Lola's middle name is for her late grandfather, Robin's dad Alan Thicke of Growing Pains fame. </p>

